---
title: Cal Smart Moroccan-Inspired Pork Chops with Jewelled Couscous and Fig Sauce
description: Sweet and savoury is the name of the game with these Moroccan-spiced succulent pork chops, topped with a delectable fig sauce,  alongside a bed of fluffy jewelled couscous.
